msgid "Cross-Site Request Forgery Prevention"
msgstr "Prevención de la falsificación de petición en sitios cruzados"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-csrf-prevention.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "https://owasp.org/www-community/attacks/csrf[Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF)] is an attack that forces an end user to execute unwanted actions on a web application in which they are currently authenticated."
msgstr "link:https://owasp.org/www-community/attacks/csrf[Cross-Site Request Forgery (CSRF)] es un ataque que fuerza a un usuario final a ejecutar acciones no deseadas en una aplicación web en la que está autenticado."

#: _versions/main/guides/security-csrf-prevention.adoc
msgid "Quarkus Security provides a CSRF prevention feature which implements https://cheatsheetseries.owasp.org/cheatsheets/Cross-Site_Request_Forgery_Prevention_Cheat_Sheet.html#double-submit-cookie[Double Submit Cookie] and <<csrf-request-header>> techniques."
msgstr ""

#: _versions/main/guides/security-csrf-prevention.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"`Double Submit Cookie` technique requires that the CSRF token sent as `HTTPOnly`, optionally signed, cookie to the client, and\n"
"directly embedded in a hidden form input of server-side rendered HTML forms, or submitted as a request header value."
msgstr "`Double Submit Cookie` La técnica requiere que el token CSRF se envíe como `HTTPOnly` , opcionalmente firmado, cookie al cliente, y directamente incrustado en una entrada de formulario oculta de los formularios HTML renderizados del lado del servidor, o enviado como un valor de cabecera de solicitud."

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/main/guides/security-csrf-prevention.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The extension consists of a xref:resteasy-reactive.adoc[RESTEasy Reactive] server filter which creates and verifies CSRF tokens in `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` and `multipart/form-data` forms and a Qute HTML form parameter provider which supports the xref:qute-reference.adoc#injecting-beans-directly-in-templates[injection of CSRF tokens in Qute templates]."
msgstr "La extensión consiste en un filtro de servidor xref:resteasy-reactive.adoc[RESTEasy Reactive] que crea y verifica los xref:qute-reference.adoc#injecting-beans-directly-in-templates[tokens CSRF] en los formularios `application/x-www-form-urlencoded` y `multipart/form-data` y un proveedor de parámetros de formulario HTML Qute que admite la xref:qute-reference.adoc#injecting-beans-directly-in-templates[inyección de tokens CSRF en las plantillas Qute] ."

